[{"_path":"/notes/agile-summit-2023-esther-leader-at-all-levels","_dir":"notes","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"en","_empty":false,"title":"Esther Derby - Leaders at All Levels","description":"","excerpt":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這個議程對我來說是 mindset 上的收穫，我特別喜歡 Context 的鑽石模型，隔日與同事閒聊時，越聊越與工作上的情境結合。界線的概念也讓我當頭棒喝，界線變來變去的危害，以及界線是觸發對話而不是高牆的概念，都讓我有種頓悟的感覺。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"領導力是塑造一個讓每個人能夠做出創意的環境"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\"Leadership is the ability to enhance the  environments so that everyone becomes empowered to contribute creatively...\""}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Context—Day-to-Day 鑽石模型"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"上面倒三角是脈絡（Context），下面三角型是日常工作（實踐）所需專業（能力與經驗）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"越資深的人有越多脈絡，較資淺的人相對少"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"管理層、領導者、與客戶接觸者有脈絡，做事的人有專業"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"讓脈絡與實踐重疊的部分就是 Diamond"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"讓中間重疊的 Diamond 擴大"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"當人數超過 20 人時，就會開始分歧化（bifurcate）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"想到幫助擴大的案例："},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Product Backlog Refinement"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Double Link Circle Meeting"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Department Meeting"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Roadmap"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"PO 與 Developer 之間；主管與成員之間；資深成員與新人之間"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/tomasli/posts/pfbid0r9t5Ct2TuissQQ689AXeLDVKdkeVBFD7wCowB8i5H3BtgiD3wFabfTCsxRMkig6ml","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"李境展 - 企業組織中的 #鑽石 指的是：背景知識（contextual... | Facebook"}]}]}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"讓小到舉凡只是「覺得怪怪」的聲音也能夠出來"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"知易行難的困境：人際風險、階級、被質問數據（但有時只是直覺）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一個作家講的故事：希臘雕塑測定是不是古物，數據顯示是，但有人覺得怪怪的，最後是發現不是，因為手彎曲的手法不是那個時代會有的風格。"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"數據能佐證，也能欺騙"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"老奶奶搬冰箱卡住門與孫子想上廁所、最後點出書櫃後有門的故事"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"New Comer 擁有還未被現況僵化的思維"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果問大老闆們，如果事情有意外，你希望什麼時候知道？多數人都會希望是立刻、馬上。"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果是這樣，那又為甚麼總是要用數據去挑戰？而不是幫助他們說出來？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"知道情況有意外時，會有情緒。但必須跟夥伴說，我不是我不是對你不高興，而是對這個情況不高興。"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"也讓我聯想：領導者可以有情緒，但要控制在對的地方去顯現。"}]}]}]}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"界線"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"鄰居為狗設置的隱形圍欄沒有埋在地下，被風吹來吹去，導致小狗不清楚何時會被電，只敢在陽台的故事"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不清楚的界線反而會讓相關人士畏手畏腳，難以成事。像是團隊就不會因此擔心、胡亂猜測，反而能夠好的直接做出決策。就像鄰居的小狗能在界線內自由發揮，而不是只敢保守的待在陽台。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"中階管理階層是最協助展開釐清界線的對話"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"界線不是一個禁止橫越的高牆，而是觸發對話的邊線。e.g."},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"居家裝潢，我們訂了 30w 預算，但這個預算我們可能只能挖東牆補西牆去滿足需求。但若是只需要提高 20% 預算到 36w，卻可以讓現在的效果翻倍到你理想中的裝潢。你是希望設計師因為高於預算都不跟你說，還是會提出來跟你討論看看？"}]}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"相信自治能力，不要把有能力的人當小朋友（只在 Team Name、點心預算有自治能力？）"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"階層的原意不是為了權力與管理，而是幫助而是幫助大家更好的工作"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\"The Original purpose of a hierarchy is always helping its originating subsystem do their job bette\" -- Donella Meadows"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"領導並不是仰賴階級，任何階層的任何人都可以是領導者"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Leadership does not depend on hierarchy. There are leaders at all levels."}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"有什麼是最小你可以幫助團隊每個人的事情？為此你需要什麼才能行動？"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"小到像是：我們在討論時，遇到鬼打牆。若是有人提出不如我們把我們的選項寫下來，透過這樣的方式揭露、讓我們發現選項並不是我們想的只有三個，而是有七個，那個人也是個領導者。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不用不用主導權，只需要自己去做。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這讓我想：去發現每個人自發領導的時刻，鼓勵他們。並嘗試讓沒有的人，有那個舞台。"}]}]}]}]}]},"title_en":"","slug":"agile-summit-2023-esther-leader-at-all-levels","aliases":["Esther Derby - Leaders at All Levels"],"created_at":"2023-06-17T16:23:28.000Z","updated_at":"2023-06-17T16:23:28.000Z","published_at":null,"tags":[],"_type":"markdown","_id":"garden:notes:agile-summit-2023-esther-leader-at-all-levels.md","_source":"garden","_file":"notes/agile-summit-2023-esther-leader-at-all-levels.md","_extension":"md","head":{"title":"Esther Derby - Leaders at All Levels - 深藏若虛"}},{"_path":"/notes/agile-summit-2023","_dir":"notes","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"en","_empty":false,"title":"敏捷高峰會 2023","description":"","excerpt":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://agile.ithome.com.tw/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Agile Summit 2023"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 是由 ACT! 台灣敏捷協會、AgileComminity.tw（台灣敏捷社群）、DevOps Taiwan、iThome 主辦的活動。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我這次是以 Speaker 的身份出席，擔任年度變革引導者座談的對談人之一。也因為大會方希望讓工作坊的機會留給會眾，所以我主要是在議程與場外活動。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"此次活動的議程如下："},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"AgileSummit2023-Sessions.png","src":"/attachments/AgileSummit2023-Sessions.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"另有雙軌的工作坊："},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"AgileSummit2023-Workshops.png","src":"/attachments/AgileSummit2023-Workshops.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我有參與到且讓我有特別收穫的議程是："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/notes/agile-summit-2023-esther-leader-at-all-levels"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Esther Derby - Leaders at All Levels"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/notes/agile-summit-2023-fong-sbe"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Fong - 拒絕再寫無效規格，來學學實例化需求！"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Esther 的議程對我來說是 mindset 上的收穫，我特別喜歡 Context 的鑽石模型，隔日與同事閒聊時，越聊越與工作上的情境結合。界線的概念也讓我當頭棒喝，界線變來變去的危害，以及界線是觸發對話而不是高牆的概念，都讓我有種頓悟的感覺。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Fong 的議程對我來說是 Specification by Example 一書的導讀，以前讀過幾次，但總無法理解透徹。經過幾年工作經驗、LeSS in Action 的洗禮，這次再透過 Fong 系統性地串聯，讓我恍然大悟。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"本文主要作為紀錄一些關鍵字的筆記，能讓我、或是有些參與者能夠回憶起，當然也參雜了一些我的想法與觀點。日後有機會再針對有感的部分寫成文章吧！"}]}]},"title_en":"Agile Summit 2023","slug":"agile-summit-2023","aliases":[],"created_at":"2023-06-17T01:35:53.000Z","updated_at":"2023-06-17T01:35:53.000Z","published_at":null,"draft":true,"tags":[],"_type":"markdown","_id":"garden:notes:agile-summit-2023.md","_source":"garden","_file":"notes/agile-summit-2023.md","_extension":"md","head":{"title":"敏捷高峰會 2023 - 深藏若虛"}}]